{"id": "ChIJFzzs8-C4woARNzCxl2jnmag", "rating": 4.3, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 899, "displayName": {"text": "Apollonia's Pizzeria", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Easygoing parlor offering thin-crust specialty pies with playful names & creative toppings.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJFzzs8-C4woARNzCxl2jnmag/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xWbGEzTlRiakJ1T1hCWE5YaE5PRVJHWkdOVGFrRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I’ve had a lot of pizza around the world, including Italy and NYC, and this is by far the BEST pizza I’ve ever had. Love it so much that it’s worth the 1.5 hour drive just for this pizza. My fav is the square slice of pepperoni. The most perfect dough and sauce 🤤 the sauce and toppings are perfectly proportioned so that you get enough with each and every bite. The crispy cheese around the edges is so good. Other favs are the thin slice vodka and pepperoni.\n\nThe cashier is super cool and personable.\n\nBE ADVISED- they’re open limited hours and are CASH ONLY.\n\nThe place is small and you can dine in by standing up and eating on the small bar located on the wall. Take some to go and reheat in the air fryer or oven. So good!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I’ve had a lot of pizza around the world, including Italy and NYC, and this is by far the BEST pizza I’ve ever had. Love it so much that it’s worth the 1.5 hour drive just for this pizza. My fav is the square slice of pepperoni. The most perfect dough and sauce 🤤 the sauce and toppings are perfectly proportioned so that you get enough with each and every bite. The crispy cheese around the edges is so good. Other favs are the thin slice vodka and pepperoni.\n\nThe cashier is super cool and personable.\n\nBE ADVISED- they’re open limited hours and are CASH ONLY.\n\nThe place is small and you can dine in by standing up and eating on the small bar located on the wall. Take some to go and reheat in the air fryer or oven. So good!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "El A", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103072254150395242527/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXu8Oaj4g3FBSSy9sGuYJaTsBUtyw96vpEWedOM1DdKberwotGZ4A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-06T18:31:07.436182967Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xWbGEzTlRiakJ1T1hCWE5YaE5PRVJHWkdOVGFrRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xWbGEzTlRiakJ1T1hCWE5YaE5PRVJHWkdOVGFrRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b8e0f3ec3c17:0xa899e76897b13037"}, {"name": "places/ChIJFzzs8-C4woARNzCxl2jnmag/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xKNmRsSjBWV05UYld4Q1gzRnRja3h3VldKU1JFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Stumbled upon this jewel of a restaurant today. The place has a definite NYC vibe. The guy that took my order was extremely helpful and friendly-5⭐️. I was excited to see they used cup & curl pepperonis, these once charred add a great depth of flavor. The thin slice crust had a wonderful taste and texture, the toppings were spot on too. I don’t normally eat thick slices but this was too appealing to pass up, another great crust and toppings. I’ll definitely visit again!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Stumbled upon this jewel of a restaurant today. The place has a definite NYC vibe. The guy that took my order was extremely helpful and friendly-5⭐️. I was excited to see they used cup & curl pepperonis, these once charred add a great depth of flavor. The thin slice crust had a wonderful taste and texture, the toppings were spot on too. I don’t normally eat thick slices but this was too appealing to pass up, another great crust and toppings. I’ll definitely visit again!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "kevin english", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108378506263646672624/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXcB--Qp5oqdmiGRHcDEsMp8_9F-Eo55EcFdiG2D9l1VS6RC1SWMw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-13T02:08:08.447115600Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xKNmRsSjBWV05UYld4Q1gzRnRja3h3VldKU1JFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xKNmRsSjBWV05UYld4Q1gzRnRja3h3VldKU1JFRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b8e0f3ec3c17:0xa899e76897b13037"}, {"name": "places/ChIJFzzs8-C4woARNzCxl2jnmag/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxMFowUjNjM0JGZVRaVGJuZHlhazVEZFZBMVlsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Tried Apollonia’s Pizzeria recently and overall it was a good experience. The staff are very friendly and welcoming, which always makes a difference.\n\nI ordered the Acapulco Gold square pizza, it was alright, just not what I was thinking it would be. It’s pretty much bread with cheese on it and a bunch of arugula :) Not bad, just different from what I expected.\n\nI’m definitely going to give them another chance and try a normal, traditional slice next time. I’ve heard great things, so I’m looking forward to it!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Tried Apollonia’s Pizzeria recently and overall it was a good experience. The staff are very friendly and welcoming, which always makes a difference.\n\nI ordered the Acapulco Gold square pizza, it was alright, just not what I was thinking it would be. It’s pretty much bread with cheese on it and a bunch of arugula :) Not bad, just different from what I expected.\n\nI’m definitely going to give them another chance and try a normal, traditional slice next time. I’ve heard great things, so I’m looking forward to it!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Russo Gasimov", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103095427529417040479/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6sfCKEgzl-LUBhk-bdU33L9z45lS3hPu81DOu367AtPMMLXw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-27T06:38:58.035913714Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxMFowUjNjM0JGZVRaVGJuZHlhazVEZFZBMVlsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxMFowUjNjM0JGZVRaVGJuZHlhazVEZFZBMVlsRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b8e0f3ec3c17:0xa899e76897b13037"}, {"name": "places/ChIJFzzs8-C4woARNzCxl2jnmag/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xUmJXSmFjV3hJUTBWTmJGWXdXR0U1UW5CQ1lsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I had an amazing experience at Apollonia Pizza! The atmosphere is really welcoming and has a great vibe. The staff were incredibly friendly and attentive. I tried the vodka square pizza, which I believe is Chicago-style, and it was absolutely delicious. I also had a triangle pie with pepperoni and pickled jalapenos, and that was equally amazing. Highly recommend this place!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I had an amazing experience at Apollonia Pizza! The atmosphere is really welcoming and has a great vibe. The staff were incredibly friendly and attentive. I tried the vodka square pizza, which I believe is Chicago-style, and it was absolutely delicious. I also had a triangle pie with pepperoni and pickled jalapenos, and that was equally amazing. Highly recommend this place!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Julio Fernandez", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117716667351248766925/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUD0_DKUXJkqYWj1ePwRDaDxd2uFpprYO_wydSoYA1UTgTitWOM=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-31T19:50:02.734936162Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xUmJXSmFjV3hJUTBWTmJGWXdXR0U1UW5CQ1lsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xUmJXSmFjV3hJUTBWTmJGWXdXR0U1UW5CQ1lsRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b8e0f3ec3c17:0xa899e76897b13037"}, {"name": "places/ChIJFzzs8-C4woARNzCxl2jnmag/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tOU1JIVlpVMjl6WWxRdFEyUnFaVTVyYW0weWFXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Best single slice of pizza I’ve had in LA in some time! Favorite was the thin slice. Wasn’t a huge fan of the square, but I think it’s just personal preference. We also tried the whole Wilshire Margherita which has chicken sausage. It was good, but wasn’t as good as the classic slice. Something about the cheese and sauce that was different, but the crispy crust carry’s all the slices.\n\nService was fast and friendly. Thankfully no lines, so the wait was short to heat up the slices (about 5-10 mins) and while pie (about 20 mins). Cash only and parking was tight but we got lucky. Happy I finally got to try this place. Will compare all others to Appolonia’s now :)", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Best single slice of pizza I’ve had in LA in some time! Favorite was the thin slice. Wasn’t a huge fan of the square, but I think it’s just personal preference. We also tried the whole Wilshire Margherita which has chicken sausage. It was good, but wasn’t as good as the classic slice. Something about the cheese and sauce that was different, but the crispy crust carry’s all the slices.\n\nService was fast and friendly. Thankfully no lines, so the wait was short to heat up the slices (about 5-10 mins) and while pie (about 20 mins). Cash only and parking was tight but we got lucky. Happy I finally got to try this place. Will compare all others to Appolonia’s now :)", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "David Cho", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109313146400701703936/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ1zM5XB7jSBjxI6NQM7bFmhpBe9fQQuwrD8lj_r-M8KX1RwQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-24T05:56:22.725829045Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tOU1JIVlpVMjl6WWxRdFEyUnFaVTVyYW0weWFXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tOU1JIVlpVMjl6WWxRdFEyUnFaVTVyYW0weWFXYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b8e0f3ec3c17:0xa899e76897b13037"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJFzzs8-C4woARNzCxl2jnmag/photos/AWCwydhlAG_ZMHMzeCwrqvJfMwP-qGW4gf8CnpoaBXQQDcCnER66dq1My0GYoS8nue5WLhNfkAFC8gd3K4trMR-ESSsM-Vqpgz3DImsWjEnpckYh8xuDaxZKAQ2xgfl9xhvnxR0lCTqBAuY7qEK0rHcmiDGXC_mspg8u1_exKaVIyzGvw84qk1ZtEmp5_y6PprJaCaeShcJ4-NNARN-Tf1btZqss3IhmYWK6WoB37ITAMSvJmAggvfj51YSIFpa0gZg5TlT_VNTq9iTk3b988dxx8XwqokhcftbzcThpR7CuHaAyu5PckB-C9IfE_e1lyCZPOGCXfn7UXPwKy2WpDasMf2qpVk-p6KfWa0hb7VAu_IA_FCGAyfdpEvjn67b2Fwzea14JTVGZ-zOqY5j8_spHKLwfUp-t2hOL55n-b6v9gShS1QbXnKT5bsj9xwUn5MNc", "widthPx": 1600, "heightPx": 1200, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Apollonia's Pizzeria", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/104837097202592654829", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkxV66CFsDW4FEJsELTrytDWS9Yd6jqer9cznbSOlKqDrWhDY=s100-p-k-no-mo"}], "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=!1e10!2sCIABIhD-Q9DgkOrY7zjLot1mDJkP&t=27&cb_client=maps_api_places.places_api&hl=en-US", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/place//data=!3m4!1e2!3m2!1sCIABIhD-Q9DgkOrY7zjLot1mDJkP!2e10!4m2!3m1!1s0x80c2b8e0f3ec3c17:0xa899e76897b13037"}, {"name": "places/ChIJFzzs8-C4woARNzCxl2jnmag/photos/AWCwydiI0iRNAc_UlQ31AdEXTQ-YJDIiuln2eJbyAxasn5bspzfJXq_P1lXsiLcYZI3U4VasgUqqO9bmFLH7MWCjRAgFfdYTLyFVEjUyYnRoApl7N4hDThXpBMUV7cAzLSY_vWNCijmHr3Tb9ihNzw